WEBVTT

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.056
sometimes eight, 10 --

00:04:31.080 --> 00:04:34.296
that would result in hair loss,

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:35.536
bald spots,

00:04:35.560 --> 00:04:37.760
sometimes even burns on the scalp.

00:04:38.440 --> 00:04:43.216
We fry our hair at temperatures
of 450 degrees Fahrenheit or higher

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:44.496
almost daily,

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:46.520
to maintain the straight look.

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:52.336
Or we simply cover our hair up
with wigs and weaves,

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:55.016
only to let our roots breathe in private

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:58.160
where no one knows
what's really going on under there.

00:04:59.520 --> 00:05:02.816
We adopted these practices
in our own communities,